summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning, amending plat 305E, Page 190 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property annexed to The City of Seattle by Ordinance 107083 from Single Family Residence Low Density (RS 9600) Zone to Single Family Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone and General Industrial (IG) Zone (C.F. 286293).
